data.description: Rare find! 3BR/3BA one-level home on Lake Hamilton, in Lakeside School District!  This is a large, completely level property consisting of one full lot and and one half lot in Cleveland Shores Subdivision.  Plenty of room to build an additional structure on the property.  The home needs a little cosmetic updating, but the location and views are the primary features of this beautiful lake property.   Two stall covered boat slip.  New roof will be installed soon.  This would make the perfect weekender or short term rental.  Better hurry!
